## üì¶ Installation

### Install via **PyPI**

```bash
pip install faiz
```

üëâ **PyPI Package:** [https://pypi.org/project/faiz/](https://pypi.org/project/faiz/)

### Or Clone via **GitHub**

```bash
git clone https://github.com/zokasta/faiz.git
cd faiz
python setup.py install
```

üëâ **GitHub Repository:** [https://github.com/zokasta/faiz](https://github.com/zokasta/faiz)

